Description:
Gain Mainframe Access
and disable security

Search for AI Core Location
in Room Database

Take Down Security Guards
and copy Digital Map
from them

Convince Caretaker to 
show you the way

Create Copy of AI
on Secure Shard

Escape after Core
Security Alert Triggered

Stick to the Shadows
and Sneak Out

Hack and take over
Security Drones
Effect Desc: +1 Grit and +1 Veil for each 3 Hacker Stat

For Every Color Node Chosen:
+10% Reward

For every Blue Node Chosen: 
+10% Reward

For each pair of Damage and Risk prevented:
+15% Reward
